title: ABSOLUTION - RUBICON 002 (2013) (c2c) (GreenManGroup-DCP)
description:
ABSOLUTION RUBICON #2
(Mature Readers)

Publisher: AVATAR PRESS

(Writer) Christos N. Gage
(Artist/Cover Artist) Daniel Gete

The Polymath is murdering everyone in his path and laying waste to the city. John Dusk is determined to take him down again, but how can you stop a madman that is immune to every form of violence he's faced in the past? Heroes fall, a legend dies, and innocents are buried beneath the tides of violence. The body count continues to build as CHRISTOS GAGE returns to his violent crime-filled and adrenaline-fueled world.

In Shops: 7/31/2013
